articles.title: About me
articles.contents:
Hi, thanks for visiting! I am Federico and I live in Buenos Aires, Argentina. I graduated in economics and have been working in data science positions slightly before the term was widely spread (or at least as spread as it is now).
In this site I will share some of my thoughts and side projects. If you wish you to contact me, you can find me at:
Twitter: [@FedeScenna](https://twitter.com/FedeScenna)
Github: FedeScenna
